WEBVTT

01:40.460 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.259 --> 01:48.750
[Episode 8]

01:49.940 --> 01:51.400
Let's talk about it later.

02:03.410 --> 02:04.100
Come back.

02:17.090 --> 02:19.610
You're the girl
from the boxing gym that day, right?

02:19.610 --> 02:20.770
So what if I was?

02:22.700 --> 02:24.579
How did you hook up with Jin Zhao?

02:25.460 --> 02:27.060
Have you two slept together?

02:27.490 --> 02:28.690
Don't talk nonsense.

02:29.020 --> 02:30.650
He and I aren't like that.

02:36.810 --> 02:37.700
And who are you?

02:39.490 --> 02:40.170
Guess.

02:41.700 --> 02:42.530
Snakey?

02:42.650 --> 02:43.810
Are you crazy?

02:44.020 --> 02:46.220
What snake? That's a dragon on my waist!

02:47.530 --> 02:48.790
So you're Dragon then.

02:57.650 --> 02:58.860
I just realized

02:59.270 --> 03:00.680
you're kinda cute,

03:01.650 --> 03:03.210
like a little bunny.

03:04.710 --> 03:05.680
I'm Wan Qing.

03:06.730 --> 03:07.420
And you?

03:10.160 --> 03:10.930
Jiang Mu.

03:12.810 --> 03:13.740
Jiang Mu.

03:16.020 --> 03:17.050
Jiang.

03:20.610 --> 03:21.700
Tell me,

03:22.579 --> 03:25.240
what's really going on
between Jin Zhao and you?

03:31.210 --> 03:32.370
Be honest.

03:34.260 --> 03:35.050
Tell me!

03:37.180 --> 03:38.240
What are you doing?

03:39.950 --> 03:40.880
Don't scare her.

03:44.370 --> 03:46.490
I'm just joking with her.

03:47.030 --> 03:47.750
Right?

03:48.630 --> 03:49.700
Why so fierce?

03:51.180 --> 03:52.650
If you think I'm fierce, get lost.

03:52.650 --> 03:53.980
No way.

03:54.420 --> 03:56.370
I just like you this way.

03:57.180 --> 03:58.260
Besides,

03:58.490 --> 04:00.210
I've only been gone for a few days,

04:00.210 --> 04:02.530
and you've already hooked up
with someone new.

04:02.530 --> 04:03.810
That's so heartless.

04:08.050 --> 04:08.740
Come on,

04:08.860 --> 04:11.320
let's go get some pork trotters.
Ignore him.

04:25.820 --> 04:27.020
Crazy, Crazy! Hurry!

04:27.090 --> 04:28.410
Clear some space, clear some space!

04:28.410 --> 04:29.940
Hot dish coming through!

04:31.770 --> 04:32.580
Jiang Mu,

04:33.180 --> 04:34.500
guess what's in here?

04:35.810 --> 04:37.470
You really made chicken soup?

04:42.030 --> 04:43.790
Brandy bought the chicken this morning,

04:43.790 --> 04:46.180
and I just stewed it for you.

04:46.490 --> 04:47.950
I didn't lie to you, right?

04:49.030 --> 04:49.870
Thank you.

04:54.480 --> 04:55.159
Brandy,

04:55.470 --> 04:57.270
come sit with me and have a drink.

05:08.770 --> 05:10.560
These pork trotters are delicious.

05:10.560 --> 05:12.090
Pass them around. Try some.

05:14.340 --> 05:15.470
Quick, give me some.

05:19.540 --> 05:20.200
Here you go.

05:20.260 --> 05:20.950
Cheers.

05:21.680 --> 05:23.610
You don't know how to eat trotters?

05:29.060 --> 05:29.900
Eat.

05:30.970 --> 05:31.970
I'll eat it later.

05:41.840 --> 05:42.590
What?

05:43.090 --> 05:44.409
I stewed this chicken for two hours,

05:44.409 --> 05:45.940
and you want the first bite?

05:46.940 --> 05:49.870
What do you even need nourishment for?
Are you crazy?

05:57.080 --> 05:58.200
Come on, come on.

05:58.780 --> 06:00.100
My bad, my bad.

06:02.990 --> 06:03.660
Sis.

06:05.540 --> 06:06.470
Please try some.

06:07.700 --> 06:08.510
Thank you.

06:13.910 --> 06:14.640
How is it?

06:15.600 --> 06:16.530
Very delicious.

06:19.690 --> 06:21.620
You glutton, really.

06:27.650 --> 06:28.850
Who's this girl with?

06:30.700 --> 06:31.700
Brandy's sister.

06:32.210 --> 06:33.680
Isn't Brandy's sister

06:34.040 --> 06:35.640
still in elementary school?

06:38.640 --> 06:39.620
Where did this beautiful little girl

06:39.620 --> 06:40.820
come from?

06:41.070 --> 06:42.530
Blood-related siblings?

06:48.330 --> 06:50.060
Well, why are you looking at me?

07:06.540 --> 07:08.470
I'm talking to you! Can't you hear?

07:09.850 --> 07:10.780
Blood-related.

07:11.500 --> 07:13.030
His blood-related sister.

07:13.280 --> 07:15.260
She's really his blood-related sister.

07:15.260 --> 07:15.850
Um...

07:15.970 --> 07:17.460
I swear on my old man,

07:17.580 --> 07:18.490
they're siblings by blood,

07:18.490 --> 07:21.090
and their bond is stronger
than anyone else's.

07:30.110 --> 07:31.970
I heard Guang and his men came here

07:32.210 --> 07:33.280
and caused trouble.

07:33.280 --> 07:34.680
What were they thinking?

07:34.850 --> 07:36.330
I called Xiang to the back

07:36.460 --> 07:37.600
and taught him a lesson.

07:37.600 --> 07:38.970
I did pretty well, huh?

07:41.970 --> 07:42.730
No need.

07:43.700 --> 07:44.970
What do you mean, "no need"?

07:44.970 --> 07:45.770
Unnecessary.

07:46.730 --> 07:49.290
Crazy Jin works for Wan's Garage?

07:51.710 --> 07:53.460
I was just looking out for our buddy.

07:53.460 --> 07:55.890
Are you eating that trotter?
If not, give it to me.

07:55.890 --> 07:56.820
I have more here.

08:06.330 --> 08:07.290
Stop that.

08:07.640 --> 08:10.440
Your hands are all greasy.
Let me wipe them for you.

08:11.910 --> 08:12.910
I can do it myself.

08:52.450 --> 08:53.710
Brandy, are you crazy?

09:21.760 --> 09:23.490
Take your time eating, sister.

09:24.040 --> 09:25.370
Be careful not to choke.

09:28.260 --> 09:29.190
Hurry up and eat.

09:30.690 --> 09:33.090
After eating,
go back to Jin Qiang's place.

09:34.850 --> 09:36.290
I haven't finished my homework yet.

09:36.290 --> 09:38.220
I'll go back to my room to finish it.

09:55.160 --> 09:56.160
Come on, Jiang Mu.

09:57.280 --> 09:58.880
Here's a big coconut for you.

09:59.560 --> 10:00.810
Thank you, Sanlai.

10:01.820 --> 10:02.730
Sanlai.

10:05.990 --> 10:06.990
Where's Jin Zhao?

10:07.730 --> 10:08.530
He's outside.

10:09.810 --> 10:12.570
Is Wan Qing his girlfriend?

10:19.690 --> 10:21.290
Brandy wouldn't be with her.

10:21.900 --> 10:22.740
Why?

10:26.260 --> 10:27.860
She's the daughter

10:28.300 --> 10:29.700
of Wan's Garage's owner.

10:31.390 --> 10:34.230
The daughter of Wan's Garage's owner...

10:34.850 --> 10:35.640
So,

10:36.290 --> 10:37.950
not going home again tonight?

10:38.500 --> 10:39.380
Of course not.

10:39.620 --> 10:40.930
I haven't finished my homework yet.

10:40.930 --> 10:42.570
I'll go home after I finish it here.

10:42.570 --> 10:44.450
Besides, the AC at home is still broken.

10:44.450 --> 10:45.450
It's boiling hot.

10:47.210 --> 10:49.600
Your AC is broken.
Then you really shouldn't go back.

10:49.600 --> 10:50.930
It must be insanely hot.

10:51.760 --> 10:53.560
I never said I wasn't going home.

10:54.790 --> 10:55.550
Really?

10:59.010 --> 11:00.580
Alright, I'm not teasing you anymore.

11:00.580 --> 11:01.710
I'll leave you to it.

11:07.840 --> 11:08.990
As I said before,

11:09.480 --> 11:11.410
if you need money, just tell me.

11:11.620 --> 11:13.950
Please don't get yourself into that mess.

11:14.220 --> 11:15.260
You're wading

11:15.260 --> 11:16.650
into deep waters.

11:17.810 --> 11:19.020
Just listen to me on this.

11:19.020 --> 11:20.380
I'd never harm you.

11:21.330 --> 11:23.330
My business is none of your concern.

11:24.730 --> 11:27.060
Have I ever bothered with
other people's business?

11:27.060 --> 11:28.320
You're unbelievable.

11:28.710 --> 11:30.660
Jin Zhao, don't push me too far.

11:32.650 --> 11:33.930
And if I do?

11:35.860 --> 11:37.170
Let me put it this way:

11:38.020 --> 11:39.690
you can't get that part you want

11:39.690 --> 11:41.050
anywhere in Manshi.

11:41.340 --> 11:43.200
My father had people buy them all.

11:43.740 --> 11:44.940
Just give in a little,

11:45.220 --> 11:46.500
and I'll help you get one.

11:46.500 --> 11:47.360
How about that?

11:49.100 --> 11:50.360
I don't need your help.

11:51.100 --> 11:52.360
I can handle it myself.

12:02.380 --> 12:03.050
Leave.

12:03.630 --> 12:05.290
Stop coming here all the time.

12:06.170 --> 12:07.140
Suit yourself.

12:07.510 --> 12:08.970
As if I wanted to come here.

12:24.650 --> 12:25.710
What are you doing?

12:25.900 --> 12:26.900
Cleaning the car.

12:28.340 --> 12:29.470
Stay away from here.

12:31.450 --> 12:32.410
Why?

12:34.100 --> 12:36.360
Can't you see there's stuff everywhere?

12:37.370 --> 12:39.030
What could you do here anyway?

12:39.580 --> 12:41.580
Why is she allowed to come here then?

12:47.520 --> 12:48.670
Are you...

12:49.570 --> 12:50.850
throwing a tantrum?

12:52.170 --> 12:53.260
What tantrum?

12:53.440 --> 12:54.480
I'm not throwing any tantrum.

12:54.480 --> 12:55.880
I have a very good temper.

12:56.170 --> 12:58.370
I'm just seeking fairness and justice.

13:00.140 --> 13:00.740
Yes,

13:01.170 --> 13:02.500
you have a great temper.

13:05.720 --> 13:08.100
You're not as even-tempered
as you used to be too!

13:08.100 --> 13:09.230
Look who's talking.

13:20.120 --> 13:21.880
Crazy works for Mr. Wan.

13:22.290 --> 13:23.530
He heard about those guys

13:23.530 --> 13:25.620
who came here the other day
to cause trouble.

13:25.620 --> 13:27.820
He gave Xiang a good beating afterward.

13:28.350 --> 13:30.710
But Jin Zhao changed the subject,

13:31.420 --> 13:34.380
probably because Wan Qing was there.

13:36.740 --> 13:39.400
There's a conflict
between Jin Zhao and Mr. Wan,

13:39.620 --> 13:41.480
and Snakey is Mr. Wan's daughter.

13:41.900 --> 13:44.020
However, her stance is unclear.

13:44.380 --> 13:46.440
She seems to care about Jin Zhao a lot.

13:46.930 --> 13:47.810
She...

13:48.690 --> 13:50.350
She has feelings for Jin Zhao.

13:51.740 --> 13:54.340
But Jin Zhao probably
isn't interested in her.

13:54.980 --> 13:55.690
Otherwise,

13:55.930 --> 13:58.390
he wouldn't have interrupted her
like that.

14:08.410 --> 14:09.530
Look at this place.

14:10.100 --> 14:11.100
So much stuff.

14:12.020 --> 14:13.220
It's dirty and messy.

14:14.090 --> 14:16.220
Aren't you afraid there might be rats?

14:21.620 --> 14:23.620
What does she mean by "deep waters"?

14:24.980 --> 14:26.440
That's not for you to know.

14:26.980 --> 14:28.780
She seems to care about you a lot.

14:36.450 --> 14:37.710
You should go home now.

14:40.260 --> 14:41.620
Sanlai said

14:42.550 --> 14:44.410
he'll leave the door open for you.

14:45.310 --> 14:46.840
Why should I go to his place?

14:53.720 --> 14:55.450
You don't want to go home again?

14:58.860 --> 14:59.570
The...

15:00.170 --> 15:01.690
The AC at home is broken.

15:02.020 --> 15:03.050
It's super hot.

15:03.220 --> 15:04.340
I can't

15:04.370 --> 15:05.810
even sleep at night.

15:07.850 --> 15:09.610
Didn't I just fix it last time?

15:10.410 --> 15:11.580
You're remembering wrong.

15:11.580 --> 15:13.040
That was the water heater.

15:16.350 --> 15:18.610
Then I'll have Sanlai go fix it tomorrow.

15:20.410 --> 15:21.260
Fix it then.

15:21.600 --> 15:23.120
No matter what gets fixed,

15:23.260 --> 15:26.060
some other appliance
will break down soon enough.

15:30.030 --> 15:31.290
Those junky appliances

15:31.290 --> 15:32.810
break down so easily.

15:33.210 --> 15:34.260
It's so hot at home.

15:34.260 --> 15:36.290
What if I get heatstroke?

15:48.530 --> 15:50.420
[Speeding Auto House]

16:24.170 --> 16:24.930
Wake up.

16:27.980 --> 16:28.770
Get up!

16:30.810 --> 16:32.530
Go away.

16:34.260 --> 16:35.920
Don't you have to go to school?

16:57.530 --> 16:58.660
I don't know the way.

16:58.930 --> 17:02.060
Where was the building
for the foundation course again?

17:04.599 --> 17:05.400
Take bus No. 8.

17:07.530 --> 17:09.400
I can't read the characters here,

17:09.520 --> 17:11.440
and I don't know which stop to get off at.

17:11.440 --> 17:13.250
What if I get kidnapped?

17:13.650 --> 17:14.810
Get off after three stops.

17:14.810 --> 17:16.470
You can count to three, right?

17:25.900 --> 17:28.900
What should I do? I'm gonna be late.

17:29.120 --> 17:30.530
I'm gonna be late.

17:30.950 --> 17:33.190
I'm gonna be late. What should I do?

17:33.580 --> 17:35.300
What should I do? I'm gonna be late!

17:35.300 --> 17:36.820
What should I do? What should I do?

17:36.820 --> 17:38.550
-And then?
-I'm late. I'm late.

17:44.340 --> 17:45.380
You'd rather sleep 10 more minutes

17:45.380 --> 17:47.040
even if it means going hungry?

17:47.530 --> 17:49.330
I can't afford to lose any sleep.

17:51.780 --> 17:53.210
The bed needs me.

18:25.060 --> 18:28.420
♪ What was it that brought me to you? ♪

18:28.800 --> 18:30.710
♪ Perhaps it was fate's design ♪

18:31.290 --> 18:35.030
♪ Through all our winding paths,
we always find each other ♪

18:32.370 --> 18:33.140
Let's go.

18:35.050 --> 18:38.650
♪ The storm turned to rain,
and everything was swept away ♪

18:38.680 --> 18:40.390
♪ Slowly, everything becomes clear ♪

18:40.410 --> 18:42.770
♪ In your gaze ♪

18:43.060 --> 18:45.020
♪ I found the answer ♪

18:45.050 --> 18:47.090
♪ There's a feeling so strong ♪

18:47.120 --> 18:50.250
♪ Our story is still unfolding ♪

18:50.390 --> 18:54.300
♪ Waiting for the perfect ending ♪

18:52.490 --> 18:53.450
I'm gonna be late, I'm gonna be late.

18:53.450 --> 18:54.140
Come here.

18:56.010 --> 18:58.460
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

18:58.480 --> 19:00.950
♪ There's a pull I cannot explain ♪

19:00.980 --> 19:04.100
♪ My eyes follow you,
my heart chases after you ♪

19:04.120 --> 19:05.930
♪ I just can't help it ♪

19:05.950 --> 19:08.400
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

19:08.430 --> 19:10.930
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

19:10.950 --> 19:13.960
♪ Sweet longing drifts on the wind ♪

19:13.980 --> 19:16.200
♪ I can feel you near ♪

19:16.220 --> 19:18.340
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

19:18.370 --> 19:20.740
♪ The road ahead ♪

19:20.770 --> 19:22.620
♪ And every step we take ♪

19:22.650 --> 19:25.320
♪ Guide us toward happiness ♪

19:25.340 --> 19:28.040
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

19:28.070 --> 19:30.630
♪ There's a pull I cannot explain ♪

19:30.650 --> 19:32.480
♪ My eyes follow you ♪

19:31.620 --> 19:32.210
I'm off to class.

19:32.210 --> 19:32.970
Wait.

19:32.500 --> 19:35.730
♪ My heart chases after you,
I just can't help it ♪

19:35.750 --> 19:37.820
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

19:36.210 --> 19:36.900
Breakfast.

19:37.840 --> 19:40.320
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

19:38.250 --> 19:39.100
Thank you.

19:40.610 --> 19:43.820
♪ Sweet memories ride upon the wind ♪

19:43.840 --> 19:46.190
♪ I can feel you near ♪

19:46.210 --> 19:48.630
♪ Because I have you by my side ♪

19:47.900 --> 19:49.540
There's a school open house in a few days.

19:48.650 --> 19:51.300
♪ Forget the sunsets, forget the tides ♪

19:49.730 --> 19:51.320
Parents are asked to attend.

19:51.320 --> 19:53.420
♪ Watch the years pass
and wander the world ♪

19:53.440 --> 19:55.550
♪ We've learned to
cherish each other more ♪

19:54.730 --> 19:55.410
Bye.

19:55.570 --> 19:58.050
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

19:58.080 --> 20:00.390
♪ The road ahead ♪

20:00.620 --> 20:02.460
♪ And every step we take ♪

20:02.530 --> 20:05.250
♪ Guide us toward happiness ♪

20:04.160 --> 20:07.320
[School Open House]

20:07.680 --> 20:11.610
♪ We'll both be there ♪

20:42.530 --> 20:43.730
Hello, may I help you?

20:45.270 --> 20:47.070
Do you sell Wankel engines here?

20:47.530 --> 20:48.530
Wankel engine...

20:49.210 --> 20:49.880
No.

20:54.580 --> 20:55.260
Take care.

21:39.100 --> 21:41.760
Would you like something to eat?
Please come in.

21:43.730 --> 21:44.660
Please sit here.

21:45.100 --> 21:46.260
What would you like to order?

21:46.260 --> 21:47.540
We have all kinds of staples.

21:47.540 --> 21:48.860
Here's the menu.

21:49.300 --> 21:51.190
No need to check the stir-fry section.

21:51.190 --> 21:52.300
We only have boiled beef,

21:52.300 --> 21:53.580
stir-fried fish, and clear soup left.

21:53.580 --> 21:54.900
Just those three dishes.

21:54.900 --> 21:56.100
Those three dishes then.

21:56.100 --> 21:56.780
Thank you.

21:57.010 --> 21:58.140
You want all of them?

21:58.930 --> 22:00.460
Okay, please wait a moment.

22:05.100 --> 22:07.060
Table 1 ordered all three

22:07.140 --> 22:08.200
remaining dishes!

22:31.010 --> 22:31.850
Here you go.

22:34.290 --> 22:36.350
First time at our restaurant, right?

22:36.380 --> 22:37.410
Our dishes are a bit spicy.

22:37.410 --> 22:38.650
I wonder if you can handle it.

22:38.650 --> 22:39.810
It's fine. I like spicy food.

22:39.810 --> 22:40.250
Here's your water.

22:40.250 --> 22:41.440
No need. I can do it myself.

22:41.440 --> 22:42.580
Okay. Here are the chopsticks.

22:42.580 --> 22:43.510
Okay, thank you.

22:45.810 --> 22:46.530
Zhao,

22:46.970 --> 22:48.010
have you eaten yet?

22:48.010 --> 22:48.680
I have.

22:49.570 --> 22:50.170
Oh, right,

22:50.490 --> 22:52.100
three more cases of beer tomorrow.

22:52.100 --> 22:52.810
Don't forget.

22:52.810 --> 22:53.450
Got it.

23:13.170 --> 23:15.140
When you're driving, you remind me of

23:15.140 --> 23:16.300
someone I know.

23:16.400 --> 23:17.730
That friend of yours...

23:18.490 --> 23:21.010
the one who uses a Wankel engine?

23:21.650 --> 23:22.250
Yes.

23:23.620 --> 23:24.900
You both look

23:25.350 --> 23:26.390
very relaxed.

23:55.090 --> 23:55.960
Half past two.

24:18.130 --> 24:19.140
Zhao, you're back.

24:19.140 --> 24:19.820
I'm back.

24:20.200 --> 24:23.000
Take some of the dumplings I made
before you leave!

24:45.080 --> 24:45.670
This...

24:46.790 --> 24:47.860
Isn't this the school uniform

24:47.860 --> 24:49.120
you treasured so much?

24:49.250 --> 24:50.540
What are you going to do with it?

24:50.540 --> 24:51.300
Mu wants it.

24:52.010 --> 24:53.690
Give it to me then. I'll wash it later.

24:53.690 --> 24:54.410
No need, Auntie Zhao.

24:54.410 --> 24:56.770
I'll wash it myself at the garage.
You go ahead.

24:56.770 --> 24:57.900
You're leaving now?

24:59.220 --> 25:00.400
Take some dumplings!

25:00.400 --> 25:01.140
No, thanks!

25:08.410 --> 25:10.470
Could the keychain Sanlai mentioned

25:10.540 --> 25:11.970
be on him?

25:20.190 --> 25:22.730
Um, I need to get up early tomorrow
for my foundation course.

25:22.730 --> 25:23.970
I don't want to trouble you.

25:23.970 --> 25:26.630
Just give me the keys.
I'll open the door myself.

25:30.550 --> 25:32.370
The AC at home still isn't fixed.

25:32.620 --> 25:35.020
Sanlai said it'll take more time
to repair.

25:35.320 --> 25:37.520
I might have to stay here again tonight.

25:42.830 --> 25:43.790
Give me the keys.

25:48.150 --> 25:49.800
It's fine. I can get them myself.

25:49.800 --> 25:50.730
They're in here?

25:51.900 --> 25:52.950
There, there, I see them.

25:52.950 --> 25:54.150
I can get them myself.

26:01.030 --> 26:02.830
What are you feeling around for?

26:09.120 --> 26:10.650
What are you talking about?

26:14.970 --> 26:17.640
Why do you always bully her
and make her mad?

26:19.120 --> 26:20.850
I don't even know why she's mad.

26:21.890 --> 26:24.690
She was just searching around
and suddenly got mad.

26:24.690 --> 26:26.640
There's nothing unusual in my pocket.

26:26.640 --> 26:28.840
Do I have gold in my pocket or something?

26:29.720 --> 26:30.540
Maybe I should put

26:30.540 --> 26:32.400
a coin in my pocket for her to find.

26:32.960 --> 26:33.810
Good idea.

26:34.230 --> 26:35.760
I'm heading back to my shop.

27:08.680 --> 27:09.600
Time to get up.

27:10.200 --> 27:12.060
It's the weekend. No class today.

27:18.860 --> 27:20.410
The ingredients are very fresh today.

27:20.410 --> 27:20.860
Yes.

27:20.860 --> 27:21.820
Mu, eat more.

27:21.900 --> 27:22.450
Okay.

27:22.730 --> 27:23.790
It's so delicious.

27:23.860 --> 27:25.860
Jiang Mu, don't just eat meat. Here!

27:25.880 --> 27:27.480
Freshly washed vegetables.

27:27.900 --> 27:29.170
Why isn't Master at the table yet?

27:29.170 --> 27:30.930
Master, come eat quickly!

27:30.930 --> 27:32.390
-Brandy, come on!
-Hurry!

27:34.750 --> 27:35.900
See if it fits.

27:45.920 --> 27:47.860
This is my master's
most treasured possession.

27:47.860 --> 27:49.620
I thought he was going to wear it
to a class reunion.

27:49.620 --> 27:51.010
I almost put it in the washing machine

27:51.010 --> 27:52.500
with his work clothes.

27:53.650 --> 27:55.380
It looks brand new.

27:55.490 --> 27:56.380
Of course.

27:56.510 --> 27:57.490
Brandy... washed it

27:57.490 --> 27:58.170
by hand.

27:58.170 --> 27:59.410
I saw it that day.

28:00.110 --> 28:01.630
No wonder.

28:01.860 --> 28:03.300
That day I saw this uniform

28:03.300 --> 28:04.010
hanging by the door,

28:04.010 --> 28:05.340
and I wanted to try it on.

28:05.450 --> 28:07.010
But your master really chewed me out,

28:07.010 --> 28:08.650
saying my hands were covered in
dog and cat hair,

28:08.650 --> 28:10.100
and wouldn't let me touch it.

28:10.100 --> 28:13.380
So he was saving it for someone.

28:23.260 --> 28:24.300
Thank you, Zhao.

28:24.920 --> 28:25.920
I can do it myself.

28:26.650 --> 28:27.540
But Jiang Mu,

28:27.970 --> 28:29.840
you must treasure this uniform.

28:30.140 --> 28:31.790
Brandy never had the chance to wear it.

28:31.790 --> 28:33.790
There's only one uniform like this.

28:34.040 --> 28:34.900
Here, eat more.

28:35.110 --> 28:35.800
Talk less.

28:36.280 --> 28:38.490
Don't worry, I'll definitely treasure it.

28:38.490 --> 28:39.580
Thank you, Brandy.

28:39.810 --> 28:41.070
Thanks again, Brandy.

28:42.050 --> 28:43.110
Just eat your food.

28:54.410 --> 28:55.650
Right on time.

28:56.100 --> 28:57.030
Mu, you're here.

28:57.330 --> 28:58.590
We can get started now.

28:59.650 --> 29:00.650
You got a uniform?

29:06.660 --> 29:08.140
Who did you borrow

29:08.400 --> 29:09.850
this uniform from?

29:10.130 --> 29:11.460
Jin Zhao. What's wrong?

29:12.780 --> 29:14.650
Your brother was a top student?

29:14.920 --> 29:17.200
Yes, I told you when we first met.

29:17.430 --> 29:18.210
I mean,

29:18.290 --> 29:20.150
he was a top student at our school?

29:21.780 --> 29:23.580
When I was in 11th grade,

29:23.820 --> 29:24.820
I heard that at our school,

29:24.820 --> 29:26.970
winners of city-level competitions
and above

29:26.970 --> 29:29.490
receive not only certificates
and scholarships

29:29.490 --> 29:31.450
but also a special uniform.

29:31.820 --> 29:33.490
The uniform looks
just like our regular one,

29:33.490 --> 29:34.970
with no obvious difference.

29:34.970 --> 29:36.450
The only difference is

29:36.930 --> 29:37.880
that around the school badge,

29:37.880 --> 29:39.600
there's a gold star.

29:46.360 --> 29:47.880
As far as I know,

29:48.170 --> 29:51.970
only one student has received
the gold star uniform in recent years.

29:53.130 --> 29:55.660
Our homeroom teacher, Mr. Ma,
once mentioned

29:55.850 --> 29:57.840
that the owner of this gold star uniform

29:57.840 --> 29:59.170
was his prized student.

30:00.320 --> 30:01.600
Looks like that person

30:01.970 --> 30:03.820
is your brother, Jin Zhao!

30:05.410 --> 30:06.370
No wonder

30:06.470 --> 30:08.290
Jin Zhao wouldn't let Sanlai try it on

30:08.290 --> 30:09.420
when he asked.

30:09.650 --> 30:11.450
Turns out it's limited edition.

30:13.780 --> 30:14.380
Nana,

30:14.500 --> 30:16.960
since you know the story
of the school badge,

30:16.970 --> 30:18.010
do you know

30:18.140 --> 30:20.140
why Jin Zhao suddenly gave up his studies?

30:20.140 --> 30:22.000
What exactly happened back then?

30:24.620 --> 30:25.690
I don't know.

30:25.770 --> 30:27.300
No one ever talked about it.

30:39.420 --> 30:40.820
I have some problems I can't solve.

30:40.820 --> 30:42.350
Could you help me with them?

30:45.110 --> 30:47.110
Sit down, and let's go through them.

31:39.170 --> 31:40.490
What competition

31:41.730 --> 31:43.650
did you win to get this uniform?

31:44.580 --> 31:46.840
City-wide physics competition trials.

31:47.460 --> 31:48.660
So you were selected?

31:50.530 --> 31:51.660
What happened then?

31:55.670 --> 31:56.520
Then nothing.

31:59.360 --> 32:00.400
Then...

32:01.860 --> 32:03.010
Back then...

32:03.640 --> 32:06.240
why didn't you take
the college entrance exam?

32:21.060 --> 32:22.010
I've made notes

32:22.730 --> 32:24.390
on all these problems for you.

32:24.690 --> 32:25.410
Take a look.

32:25.620 --> 32:27.350
Ask me if you don't understand.

32:38.870 --> 32:39.700
Jiang Mu!

32:40.820 --> 32:41.900
-Sanlai.
-Stop studying.

32:41.900 --> 32:43.500
You're gonna fry your brain.

32:44.810 --> 32:45.870
Chocolate flavor.

32:48.250 --> 32:50.510
How did you know I like chocolate flavor?

32:50.620 --> 32:51.620
Brandy told me.

32:53.030 --> 32:53.880
Forget about him.

32:53.880 --> 32:55.480
I'll take you somewhere fun.

32:56.310 --> 32:57.070
Where?

32:57.590 --> 32:58.120
Let's go.

32:59.900 --> 33:01.760
I'll show you a magic trick later.

33:05.650 --> 33:06.540
Linda!

33:07.450 --> 33:09.010
She's so adorable.

33:09.730 --> 33:11.860
Linda, why are you being so good today?

33:12.010 --> 33:12.970
Come on, come on!

33:16.960 --> 33:17.960
Come on, twirl!

33:20.420 --> 33:21.070
Go play.

33:23.390 --> 33:24.340
How did you do that?

33:24.340 --> 33:25.340
It's so adorable!

33:25.490 --> 33:26.880
Linda has been with me for years.

33:26.880 --> 33:29.040
No wonder you're so close.

33:30.040 --> 33:30.720
Jiang Mu.

33:36.140 --> 33:37.540
Are these her puppies?

33:37.570 --> 33:38.160
Yes,

33:38.330 --> 33:40.530
Xishi just gave birth to these puppies.

33:41.340 --> 33:42.380
Xishi.

33:43.450 --> 33:45.060
Congratulations, Xishi.

33:52.120 --> 33:53.120
What about that one?

33:53.120 --> 33:54.860
Why isn't its mom taking care of it?

33:54.860 --> 33:56.730
Goldie was barely breathing
when he was born,

33:56.730 --> 33:58.210
so Xishi abandoned him at the door.

33:58.210 --> 33:59.470
I went and rescued him.

34:00.790 --> 34:01.980
Poor puppy.

34:03.140 --> 34:04.800
-Come on, Goldie!
-Poor baby.

34:07.040 --> 34:07.910
Come on.

34:09.080 --> 34:10.080
Take a look at him.

34:11.989 --> 34:13.120
Little one.

34:16.780 --> 34:17.860
Hello there.

34:17.940 --> 34:19.739
I'll get him something to drink.

34:22.730 --> 34:23.920
You're lying down.

34:24.550 --> 34:25.679
He lay down.

34:26.860 --> 34:28.389
He seems to really like you.

34:30.000 --> 34:31.060
Here, you feed him.

34:33.540 --> 34:34.860
Time for some water.

34:35.739 --> 34:36.860
Just a little bit.

34:43.290 --> 34:44.489
Slow down, slow down.

34:47.010 --> 34:49.340
When I was little, I met

34:49.739 --> 34:51.650
a little yellow dog in my neighborhood.

34:51.650 --> 34:52.969
It followed me all the way home.

34:52.969 --> 34:54.830
But my mom wouldn't let me keep it.

34:58.740 --> 34:59.870
You can't have a dog!

35:00.160 --> 35:00.990
Get rid of it.

35:07.860 --> 35:09.780
Zhao, what should we do about the puppy?

35:09.780 --> 35:11.100
It needs a home.

35:11.490 --> 35:12.610
How about...

35:14.570 --> 35:15.930
we hide it?

35:16.740 --> 35:17.490
That works.

35:19.260 --> 35:19.820
Let's go.

35:19.900 --> 35:20.540
Okay.

35:49.570 --> 35:50.900
-Puppy.
-Puppy.

35:51.050 --> 35:51.930
Little puppy.

35:54.080 --> 35:55.560
Little puppy. Woof, woof.

35:56.740 --> 35:57.800
Where's the puppy?

36:05.920 --> 36:07.690
Zhao, where's the puppy?

36:09.020 --> 36:09.750
I don't know.

36:09.860 --> 36:11.130
Did it get lost?

36:11.300 --> 36:12.700
Could it be in danger?

36:13.740 --> 36:14.860
It won't be in danger.

36:14.860 --> 36:15.740
Don't worry.

36:16.850 --> 36:18.000
There it is. Let's go.

36:18.000 --> 36:18.810
Come with me.

36:21.090 --> 36:22.300
Later, Jin Zhao and I

36:22.300 --> 36:24.340
gave that puppy a name.

36:24.450 --> 36:25.780
We called it Lightning.

36:26.270 --> 36:28.380
I never saw it again after that.

36:30.490 --> 36:31.740
Would you like to keep him?

36:31.740 --> 36:32.870
I can give him to you.

36:35.860 --> 36:36.570
Forget it.

36:36.770 --> 36:38.810
I don't have a place to keep him now.

36:42.870 --> 36:44.130
You're thirsty again.

36:50.750 --> 36:51.500
Let's go!

36:52.690 --> 36:53.520
Coming!

36:55.390 --> 36:57.720
Puppy, I have to leave now.

36:57.960 --> 36:59.490
I'll come see you next time.

36:59.900 --> 37:01.160
If you want to keep him,

37:01.340 --> 37:02.270
there's a place.

37:04.520 --> 37:05.400
Go ask Brandy.

37:07.510 --> 37:08.470
Would that work?

38:01.410 --> 38:02.970
You've been staring at me this whole time.

38:02.970 --> 38:04.230
What do you want to say?

38:05.610 --> 38:07.410
I just saw the golden retriever's

38:07.410 --> 38:09.340
puppy at Sanlai's store.

38:10.760 --> 38:11.870
It's so adorable.

38:17.050 --> 38:18.090
Sanlai said

38:18.180 --> 38:19.260
that the puppy was abandoned

38:19.260 --> 38:20.780
by its mom the moment it was born.

38:20.780 --> 38:22.140
He saved its life.

38:22.490 --> 38:23.740
And it seems...

38:24.310 --> 38:26.590
Xishi doesn't like it very much either.

38:28.960 --> 38:30.610
Don't you think that's sad?

38:36.870 --> 38:38.200
He just makes up a story,

38:38.490 --> 38:39.940
and you get all emotional about it.

38:39.940 --> 38:40.930
Why don't you ask Sanlai

38:40.930 --> 38:42.010
how he saved it?

38:49.820 --> 38:50.880
You want to keep it?

38:55.130 --> 38:56.460
Out of his four puppies,

38:56.850 --> 38:58.360
two pretty good ones

38:58.520 --> 39:00.120
have already been reserved.

39:00.690 --> 39:02.950
He's giving you one of the two
that won't sell,

39:02.950 --> 39:05.200
so you can ask me to keep it at my place.

39:05.540 --> 39:07.470
That way, you'll cover the dog food

39:07.560 --> 39:09.090
and grooming costs for him.

39:09.610 --> 39:10.470
Are you stupid?

39:12.610 --> 39:13.700
If I pay for all the dog food

39:13.700 --> 39:15.220
and grooming

39:15.610 --> 39:17.590
and keep it at your place temporarily,

39:17.590 --> 39:19.120
would that be okay with you?

39:22.260 --> 39:23.460
And what about later?

39:24.530 --> 39:26.530
When you have to leave in the future,

39:26.880 --> 39:28.180
would you take it with you

39:28.180 --> 39:29.240
or just abandon it?

39:32.490 --> 39:34.400
Since you're going to leave anyway,

39:34.400 --> 39:35.860
I advise you not to keep it.

39:35.860 --> 39:37.990
It'll be harder when you get attached.

39:46.880 --> 39:49.010
That's how you really think, isn't it?

39:51.970 --> 39:54.300
Since we decided to
live separately back then,

39:54.300 --> 39:56.230
why bother with more connections?

39:58.180 --> 39:59.820
We're not real siblings,

40:00.450 --> 40:02.180
so why bother staying in touch?

40:02.720 --> 40:03.740
If we stay too close

40:03.740 --> 40:04.690
and develop bonds,

40:04.690 --> 40:06.750
it'll just become more troublesome!

40:07.330 --> 40:08.990
That's what you think, right?

40:13.560 --> 40:14.640
I have a name!

40:19.090 --> 40:21.350
You're getting this angry
just because I won't let you keep a dog?

40:21.350 --> 40:23.210
Is it really worth it over a puppy?

40:24.050 --> 40:25.340
It's not just a puppy.

40:25.900 --> 40:30.030
It's a poor little thing, unwanted
by its father and unloved by its mother!

40:42.040 --> 40:45.590
[Pet Home]

40:56.230 --> 40:56.900
Brandy!

41:01.050 --> 41:02.450
Why are you back so early?

41:10.240 --> 41:11.970
When will this puppy be weaned?

41:14.530 --> 41:15.490
No way.

41:15.520 --> 41:17.400
All it took was a dog to test you?

41:19.330 --> 41:21.390
Don't you have anything better to do?

41:23.570 --> 41:24.860
Let me ask you something.

41:24.860 --> 41:26.970
If Jiang Mu really falls for you,

41:27.120 --> 41:28.180
would you treat her

41:28.480 --> 41:30.540
as coldly as you treat everyone else?

41:37.210 --> 41:37.810
Would you?

41:37.930 --> 41:38.540
Get lost.

41:40.300 --> 41:41.180
He told us to get lost.

41:41.180 --> 41:42.310
Then let's get lost.

41:42.610 --> 41:44.690
We're going, and we're going home.

41:59.560 --> 42:02.950
[Speeding Auto House]

42:14.820 --> 42:15.490
Jiang Mu!

42:16.240 --> 42:16.910
Come here.

42:26.410 --> 42:27.610
Look at your fur baby.

42:27.800 --> 42:29.320
Hasn't he gotten bigger?

42:33.530 --> 42:34.610
What fur baby?

42:37.700 --> 42:39.030
Brandy didn't tell you?

42:39.260 --> 42:39.970
This dog

42:40.430 --> 42:41.240
is yours now.

42:42.570 --> 42:43.380
Really?

42:43.570 --> 42:45.370
Jin Zhao agreed to let me keep it?

42:47.530 --> 42:48.530
Doggie!

42:48.720 --> 42:50.720
Come here, let me hold you.

42:52.750 --> 42:54.710
Jin Zhao agreed to let me keep you!

42:55.380 --> 42:56.310
You smell so bad.

42:56.450 --> 42:57.510
How long has it been since his last bath?

42:57.510 --> 42:58.440
He never had one.

42:58.820 --> 43:00.490
You've never had a bath.

43:00.630 --> 43:02.190
What name should I give you?

43:05.590 --> 43:06.860
Isn't he cute?

43:15.460 --> 43:18.120
Sanlai said you agreed to
let me keep him, right?

43:24.250 --> 43:25.330
How about

43:25.660 --> 43:27.260
we call it Lightning too?

43:33.490 --> 43:35.090
Lightning is still little.

43:35.300 --> 43:38.160
I need to stay here
and take care of him for a few days.

43:47.000 --> 43:48.340
I'm so happy!

43:48.410 --> 43:50.340
Thank you for letting me keep him!

43:56.390 --> 43:57.080
Thank me?

43:58.470 --> 43:59.350
That formally?

44:00.420 --> 44:02.020
How are you going to thank me?

44:02.770 --> 44:04.030
How would you like me to thank you?

44:03.420 --> 44:05.600
♪ What would I do ♪

44:05.620 --> 44:08.100
♪ If I have 45 minutes? ♪

44:08.010 --> 44:08.700
Come on.

44:08.650 --> 44:11.350
♪ Would I write a song? ♪

44:10.050 --> 44:11.090
Go ahead, call me.

44:11.490 --> 44:12.330
Call you what?

44:11.840 --> 44:13.990
♪ I don't think so ♪

44:13.030 --> 44:14.030
What do you think?

44:15.550 --> 44:17.820
♪ What would I do ♪

44:17.880 --> 44:20.240
♪ If I have 70 seconds? ♪

44:20.510 --> 44:23.240
♪ Would I get a drink or two? ♪

44:23.780 --> 44:26.250
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

44:27.070 --> 44:30.260
♪ I'd rather get on that bus ♪

44:30.780 --> 44:33.480
♪ Find you where you are ♪

44:33.860 --> 44:34.700
Brother.

44:33.950 --> 44:36.200
♪ To talk about the cloud ♪

44:36.390 --> 44:39.050
♪ That looks just like a kangaroo ♪

44:39.820 --> 44:42.800
♪ And the old man on the street ♪

44:40.570 --> 44:41.500
I can't hear you.

44:42.050 --> 44:43.570
Brother! Brother!

44:43.130 --> 44:45.970
♪ Sat there with his dog ♪

44:44.090 --> 44:45.340
Brother!

44:46.380 --> 44:48.680
♪ Asking you if you're willing ♪

44:47.410 --> 44:48.630
Brother, come on! Let's go!

44:48.630 --> 44:49.790
Let me take you out to play, Brother!

44:48.700 --> 44:51.170
♪ To accompany me too ♪

44:50.540 --> 44:52.670
I'll take my brother out to play first.

44:56.670 --> 44:57.690
What are you looking at?

44:57.690 --> 44:59.920
♪ Would you like that? ♪

45:00.590 --> 45:03.500
♪ Would you like that? ♪

45:19.240 --> 45:20.120
Did I scare you?

45:21.820 --> 45:22.660
Don't worry.

45:23.070 --> 45:24.270
I know what I'm doing.

45:27.480 --> 45:28.940
Is this Jin Zhao's new dog?

45:29.130 --> 45:30.130
This is my dog.

45:30.250 --> 45:31.650
He's just boarding here.

45:32.060 --> 45:32.920
What about you?

45:33.950 --> 45:35.810
Also boarding here temporarily?

45:43.210 --> 45:44.010
You, come out.

45:44.040 --> 45:45.170
I need to talk to you.

46:08.980 --> 46:10.240
This apple is so sweet.

46:13.320 --> 46:14.250
I want one too.

46:15.610 --> 46:16.310
Thank you.

46:20.130 --> 46:22.390
Have your father come talk to me himself.

46:22.610 --> 46:23.300
What?

46:23.690 --> 46:25.290
He's my father after all.

46:25.660 --> 46:27.260
-Can't you at least…
-Apple.

46:28.300 --> 46:29.590
I don't like soft apples.
